        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\cos^2\\theta - \\sin^2\\theta\n           = \\cos\\theta\\sin\\theta(\\cos\\theta+\\sin\\theta)\\)</span>.</p>\n<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\cos\\theta + \\sin\\theta = 0 \\iff\n           \\theta\\equiv -\\frac\\pi4 (\\mathrm{mod}\\, \\pi)\\)</span>.</p>\n<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\cos\\theta-\\sin\\theta = \\cos\\theta\\sin\\theta  \\Rightarrow \n           (\\cos\\theta\\sin\\theta)^2 + 2\\cos\\theta\\sin\\theta = 1  \\Rightarrow \n           \\begin{cases}\\cos\\theta = \\frac {\\sqrt{2\\sqrt2-1} + \\sqrt2 - 1}2 \\cr\n        \n                  \\sin\\theta = \\frac {\\sqrt{2\\sqrt2-1} - \\sqrt2 + 1}2.\\end{cases}\\)</span></p>\n<p>Les valeurs trouvées conviennent.</p>\n"
